t, he explains, \"I always say the law was meant to be interpreted in a lenient manner.\"',6.82919,'United States of America','1963-05-29',10000000,112,'English',7.5,66,'Action','Drama','Western','alcoholism','ranchers','rancher\r'),(1180,'Robot & Frank','http://robotandfrank-film.com/','A delightful dramatic comedy, a buddy picture, and, for good measure, a heist film. Curmudgeonly old Frank lives by himself. His routine involves daily visits to his local library, where he has a twinkle in his eye for the librarian. His grown children are concerned about their father’s well-being and buy him a caretaker robot. Initially resistant to the idea, Frank soon appreciates the benefits of robotic support – like nutritious meals and a clean house – and eventually begins to treat his robot like a true companion. With his robot’s assistance, Frank’s passion for his old, unlawful profession is reignited, for better or worse.',23.4191,'United States of America','2012-08-16',3325038,85,'English',6.8,450,'Science Fiction','Comedy','Drama','friendship','robot','senior citizen\r'),(1192,'Stonewall','https://twitter.com/Stonewall_Movie','\"Stonewall\" is a drama about a young man in New York caught up during the 1969 Stonewall Riots, a pivotal event widely considered the starting point for the modern gay civil rights movement.',5.16023,'United States of America','2015-09-18',187674,129,'English',5.2,32,'Drama','','','stonewall riot','','\r'),(1204,'I Spit on Your Grave','','A remake of the 1979 controversial cult classic, I Spit on Your Grave retells the horrific tale of writer Jennifer Hills who takes a retreat from the city to a charming cabin in the woods to start on her next book. But Jennifer\'s presence in the small town attracts the attention of a few morally deprived locals led by Johnny, the town\'s service station owner, his two co-workers, Andy and Stanley, who along with their socially and mentally challenged friend Matthew, set out one night to teach this city girl a lesson.',26.2818,'United States of America','2010-06-17',572809,108,'English',6.3,519,'Thriller','Crime','Horror','rape','fondling','revenge\r'),(1205,'The Conversation','','Surveillance expert Harry Caul (Gene Hackman) is hired by a mysterious client\'s brusque aide (Harrison Ford) to tail a young couple, Mark (Frederic Forrest) and Ann (Cindy Williams). Tracking the pair through San Francisco\'s Union Square, Caul and his associate Stan (John Cazale) manage to record a cryptic conversation between them. Tormented by memories of a previous case that ended badly, Caul becomes obsessed with the resulting tape, trying to determine if the couple are in danger.',20.8103,'United States of America','1974-04-07',4420000,113,'English',7.5,372,'Crime','Drama','Mystery','san francisco','paranoia','audio tape\r'),(1207,'Waitress','','Jenna is a pregnant, unhappily married waitress in the deep south. She meets a newcomer to her town and falls into an unlikely relationship as a last attempt at happiness.',9.67299,'United States of America','2007-05-25',22179430,108,'English',6.7,129,'Comedy','','','waitress','unwillingly pregnant','woman director\r'),(1220,'Da Sweet Blood of Jesus','','A movie about human beings who are addicted to blood.',4.48058,'United States of America','2014-06-22',0,123,'English',4.1,13,'Thriller','Comedy','Romance','','','\r'),(1227,'Dr. No','http://www.mgm.com/#/our-titles/566/Dr.-No','In the film that launched the James Bond saga, Agent 007 battles mysterious Dr. No, a scientific genius bent on destroying the U.S. space program. As the countdown to disaster begins, Bond must go to Jamaica, where he encounters beautiful Honey Ryder, to confront a megalomaniacal villain in his massive island headquarters.',48.9015,'Jamaica','1962-10-04',59600000,110,'English',6.9,940,'Adventure','Action','Thriller','london england','england','assassination\r'),(1247,'Celeste & Jesse Forever','http://www.celesteandjesse.com','Celeste and Jesse met in high school and got married young. They laugh at the same jokes and finish each other’s sentences. They are forever linked in their friends’ minds as the perfect couple – she, a high-powered businesswoman and budding novelist; he, a free spirit who keeps things from getting boring. Their only problem is that they have decided to get divorced. Can their perfect relationship withstand this minor setback?',9.43643,'United States of America','2012-08-03',3094813,91,'English',6.4,163,'Comedy','Drama','Romance','relationship problems','male female relationship','divorce\r'),(1257,'The Maid\'s Room','','Drina, a young immigrant working as a live-in maid for a wealthy Long Island family, finds herself entangled in the family\'s web of dark secrets once she begins to suspect her employer\'s son has committed a terrible crime.',1.50169,'United States of America','2014-08-08',0,98,'English',4.8,4,'Thriller','','','','','\r'),(1260,'Open Water','','Two divers are left out at sea without a boat. There’s nothing but water for miles, unless they look at what’s underneath them...',15.6119,'United States of America','2004-08-06',54667954,79,'English',5.4,315,'Drama','Thriller','','diving','cataclysm','nightmare\r'),(1263,'Bloody Sunday','','The dramatised story of the Irish civil rights protest march on January 30 1972 which ended in a massacre by British troops.',7.33069,'Ireland','2002-01-16',773228,107,'English',7.2,53,'Action','Adventure','Drama','northern ireland','independent film','civil rights\r'),(1275,'Mad Max','','In a dystopian future Australia, a vicious biker gang murders a cop\'s family, and makes his fight with them personal.',33.1422,'Australia','1979-04-12',100000000,93,'English',6.6,1213,'Adventure','Action','Thriller','chain','baby','bridge\r'),(1276,'Middle of Nowhere','','\'Middle of Nowhere\' follows a woman named Ruby who lost her husband to incarceration and lost herself in the process.',2.83654,'United States of America','2012-10-12',0,101,'English',6.6,7,'Drama','','','prison','w